Windows下微服务使用：
1.下载相关包：
    go get -u -v github.com/go-log/log
    go get -u -v github.com/gorilla/handlers
    go get -u -v github.com/gorilla/mux
    go get -u -v github.com/gorilla/websocket
    go get -u -v github.com/mitchellh/hashstructure
    go get -u -v github.com/nlopes/slack
    go get -u -v github.com/pborman/uuid
    go get -u -v github.com/serenize/snaker

    go get -u -v github.com/hashicorp/consul
    go get -u -v github.com/miekg/dns
    go get -u -v github.com/micro/micro

2.编译micro文件：
    1.终端下 cd github.com/micro/micro
    2.go build -o micro main.go

3.protobuf插件下载：
    1.go get github.com/golang/protobuf
    2.进入github.com/golang/protobuf/protoc-gen-go
    3.go build .
    4.go get -u github.com/micro/protoc-gen-micro



Linux下微服务使用：
1.先装Protoc
    $ wget https://github.com/protocolbuffers/protobuf/releases/download/v3.20.0/protobuf-all-3.20.0.zip

    $ unzip protoc-all-3.20.0.zip

    $ cd protobuf-all-3.20.0

    $ ./configure

    $ make

    $ make install

    $ protoc --version

    异常：

    有些依赖没有安装， 大部分有提示：

    // 例如：make => No targets specified and no makefile found. Stop.

    sudo apt update

    sudo apt install gcc

    apt install gcc build-essential

    // make install => no permission

    sudo make install

    // protoc --version => no such file or directory

    在命令行执行：sudo ldconfig

2.  $ go get github.com/golang/protobuf

    $ cd github.com/golang/protobuf/protoc-gen-go

    $ go build .

3.将protoc-gen-go放入gopath/bin/目录下

4.编写hello.proto测试
        syntax = "proto3";

        option go_package="./;hello";
        package hello;

        message Hello {

            string name = 1;
            int32 age = 2;
            string addr = 3;

        }

5.protoc --go_out=./ hello.proto                  针对rpc生成go文件
  protoc --go_out=plugins=grpc:. hello.proto      针对grpc生成go文件

6.下载go-micro相关包
    go get -u -v github.com/go-log/log
    go get -u -v github.com/gorilla/handlers
    go get -u -v github.com/gorilla/mux
    go get -u -v github.com/gorilla/websocket
    go get -u -v github.com/mitchellh/hashstructure
    go get -u -v github.com/nlopes/slack
    go get -u -v github.com/pborman/uuid
    go get -u -v github.com/serenize/snaker

    go get -u -v github.com/hashicorp/consul
    go get -u -v github.com/miekg/dns

7.下载go-micro
    go get -u -v github.com/micro/micro

    $ cd github.com/micro/micro

    $ go build -o micro main.go